00:12:49.970 --> 00:12:53.960 align:middle line:84%
So the artist now has
an image or rendering--

00:12:53.960 --> 00:12:56.510 align:middle line:84%
from the girl's
memory in the dreams--

00:12:56.510 --> 00:12:59.780 align:middle line:84%
of the man that she
