00:13:45.380 --> 00:13:46.490 align:middle line:90%
He was tried.

00:13:46.490 --> 00:13:49.040 align:middle line:84%
He was convicted,
sentenced, and he is now

00:13:49.040 --> 00:13:53.300 align:middle line:84%
serving time for the
murder of this young girl.

00:13:53.300 --> 00:13:57.860 align:middle line:84%
And it is only possible
because the memory

00:13:57.860 --> 00:14:01.040 align:middle line:84%
of the girl who was
killed was preserved

00:14:01.040 --> 00:14:03.230 align:middle line:84%
in the cells of her
heart that are now

00:14:03.230 --> 00:14:07.440 align:middle line:84%
in the body of the
