states for ourselves.

00:17:40.880 --> 00:17:44.010 align:middle line:90%
We are self-healing beings.

00:17:44.010 --> 00:17:46.150 align:middle line:84%
What kind of healing
am I talking about?

00:17:46.150 --> 00:17:48.200 align:middle line:84%
When we talk about
subconscious, why

00:17:48.200 --> 00:17:51.560 align:middle line:84%
