six years old, we

00:18:00.040 --> 00:18:03.790 align:middle line:84%
begin to absorb
from our environment

00:18:03.790 --> 00:18:07.540 align:middle line:84%
patterns of personality,
patterns of behavior

00:18:07.540 --> 00:18:09.040 align:middle line:90%
from our caregivers--

00:18:09.040 --> 00:18:11.200 align:middle line:84%
maybe our parents, maybe
our adopted parents,

00:18:11.200 --> 00:18:13.240 align:middle line:84%
maybe our aunts and
uncles or grandparents,

00:18:13.240 --> 00:18:15.280 align:middle line:90%
