00:18:34.720 --> 00:18:37.720 align:middle line:84%
We absorb these
patterns unconsciously

00:18:37.720 --> 00:18:40.390 align:middle line:84%
so that we learn how to
respond to the world.

00:18:40.390 --> 00:18:41.860 align:middle line:90%
Here's the deal.

